    nn.dense + nn.bias_add + nn.relu → fused.dense_bias_relu
    nn.dense + nn.bias_add → fused.dense_bias

  After fusion:
@main(%x: Tensor[(1, 784), float32], %target: Tensor[(1), float32]) → Tensor[(1), float32] {
  %0 = fused.dense_bias_relu(%x, meta[param_0], meta[param_1])  // [1,256]  /* fused: nn.dense → nn.bias_add → nn.relu */
  %1 = fused.dense_bias(%0, meta[param_2], meta[param_3])  // [1,10]  /* fused: nn.dense → nn.bias_add */
  %2 = cross_entropy(%1, %target)  // [1]
}

  Summary: 3 total ops, 2 fused
    nn.dense+nn.bias_add → fused.dense_bias
    nn.dense+nn.bias_add+nn.relu → fused.dense_bias_relu

